a shave and a haircut used to cost nothing if 
you were a united states senator and were shaved and trimmed in the 
united states senate barber shop 
and when one reformminded senator tried to eliminate free 
senatorial shaving and hair cutting 37 years ago his 
shavedforfree colleagues rebelled 
