said he took over to halt burmas social chaos and ensure the 
elections were held 
on monday soldiers enforcing saw maungs ban on public 
gatherings shot monks students government workers and other 
unarmed demonstrators reporters conservatively estimated at least 
100 dead about 40 demonstrators and 17 soldiers died in clashes 
sunday 
