me what brailles like she said we planned the book to get 
rid of the gap between sighted and blind children we want a 
sighted child to know what braille feels like and a blind child to 
be able to feel the letters that were seeing maybe that way we 
can get rid of some of the prejudice 
prejudice is a subject mrs shank knows well 
because im black some people might ask why im not doing 
